                <note rend="inline" type="source">767.68119T&amp;M/13: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Special Mission at Lausanne</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-12-07T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 7, 1922—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>31. Your 64, December 6, 2 p.m.</p>
                <p>I am much gratified at the manner in which you have presented this Government’s
                    views in regard to the question of the freedom of the Straits.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
